            <p  class='no-italics' >
Koyama sighs and gets back to leaning on the wall.  Arizumi and Kirarise talking about… how much they love me???<br>
<br>
Arizumi giggles. “We love you, Shishido!”<br>
What the fuck???<br>
<br>
Koyama leans on the wall with a look of jealousy, as Amasuki is raging over the game she’s playing with Izomi and Kanenako.<br>
<br>
“Fucking stupid ass game! Why am I dying to nothing???”<br>
<br>
I chuckle a bit to myself. These waifus really are like how I designed them…I can’t believe this is real…<br>
<br>
I take another look at Koyoma, who’s leaning on the wall. An idea starts forming in my brain as my neurons activate. Hmm…. how would this play out?<br>
<br>
I walk over to her as she starts talking.<br>
<br>
“What do you want, Michi-”<br>
<br>
DON!<br>
<br>
I do a kabedon and lean in close, as she starts blushing. All the waifus are looking at us two.<br>
<br>
“W-W-W-what???”<br>
<br>
I lean in closer. Our lips are centimeters apart. She blushes harder.<br>
<br>
“M-M-M-M-Michio-me… I… I… y-you…”<br>
<br>
I mentally prepare myself for what I’m gonna do. Here goes nothing…<br>
<br>
“You look so cute when you’re shy, Koyoma…”<br>
<br>
She blushes so hard she becomes a tomato.<br>
<br>
“EH?!?!??!??!!?”<br>
<br>
The 6 other waifus snicker to themselves. Ryotose speaks up.<br>
<br>
“I think Michio-me’s right about you being cute, Koyoma~”<br>
<br>
SHOOM<br>
<br>
I look to see Koyoma has escaped from the kabedon position by sliding, as I turn around to meet her scowling face.<br>
<br>
“W-W-What was t-that for, i-i-idiot???”<br>
<br>
GULP<br>
<br>
I think she’s mad…<br>
<br>
GULP<br>
<br>
I might’ve fucked up really badly right now…<br>
<br>
BA-DUM BA-DUM<br>
<br>
Koyoma runs out of the room while screaming.<br>
<br>
“Idiooooooooot!”<br>
<br>
Ryotose follows her as she mocks her. “Awwww, is the tomato running away?”<br>
<br>
BA-DUM BA-DUM<br>
<br>
ba-dum ba-dum<br>
<br>
My heart calms down. I don’t think my “idea” was a good one…<br>
<br>
<br>
